# Code owners for flckd.
#
# With "Require review from Code Owners" enabled on protected branches, a code
# owner must approve PRs that touch files they own. `*` makes @bruschill the
# owner of everything.
#
# NOTE: GitHub does not let a PR author satisfy their own code-owner review. PRs
# authored by @bruschill therefore need either a second reviewer or an admin
# bypass to merge (`gh pr merge <n> --admin`). CODEOWNERS is read from the base
# branch, so this takes effect for PRs opened after it lands on `main`.
* @bruschill
